data.description: SOLD AS IS. Charming Farmhouse style home on corner lot in established downtown Sanger. Upon entering you are greeted with wide plank wood like floors, windows that over look your front yard and flows into your Kitchen and dining room. Kitchen hosts Granite counter tops, glazed cabinets, Travertine backsplash, gas cooking, complementary tile floors and enough room for a full size Kitchen dining table! Flex room is located just off the dining room and has it's own private entrance! 2 additional bed rooms and Primary room are tucked down the hallway just arms length away from the full size bathroom with coordinating tile accents! Out back you have a great sized backyard with a storage shed, cozy covered sitting area with plenty of room to entertain or just to take the day in! Don't wait to see this adorable home! HOME IS BEING SOLD AS IS WITH NO REPAIRS, POSSIBLE SHORT SALE. SELLERS WAITING ON APPROVAL FROM​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ BANK
